<textList name="TEXT_ABC_LANIUS">
	<text>As you jump into the system, your computer feeds detailed sensor information on your hunt. It’s a Lanius vessel, you should be able to claim its cargo if you empty it of occupants. As your ship roars into weapons range, the knifelike edges of your prey shine in the starlight, a beautiful spectacle for such exotic game.</text>
	<text>As you jump into the system, your computer feeds detailed sensor information on your hunt. It’s a Lanius vessel, you should be able to claim its cargo if you empty it of occupants. Once you make it into range they hail you. “Scrap having, you is wanting trade?” Once you power up weapons they figure you aren’t here to share pleasantries.</text>
	<text>As you jump into the system, your computer feeds detailed sensor information on your hunt. It’s a Lanius vessel, you should be able to claim its cargo if you empty it of occupants. The fires of your engines burn bright as you intercept the bladed vessel in close combat, it’s time to claim your prize.</text>
	<text>As you jump into the system, your computer feeds detailed sensor information on your hunt. It’s a Lanius vessel, you should be able to claim its cargo if you empty it of occupants. You tear into weapons range with scrap on your mind, the pure metal vessel ahead of you ripe with loot.</text>
</textList>
